1. Napolju je veoma *mračno*. (It's very dark outside.)
2. Prošla je kroz *mračnu* uličicu. (She went through a dark alley.)
3. Teško je raditi u *mračnoj* prostoriji. (It's difficult to work in a dark room.)
4. Film je imao *mračan* kraj. (The movie had a dark ending.)
5. Njegov pogled je bio *mračan* i sumnjičav. (His gaze was dark and suspicious.)
6. Prošli smo kroz *mračne* doba. (We went through dark times.)
7. Ulica je bila *mračna* i pusta. (The street was dark and deserted.)
8. U *mračnom* uglu sobe, ležao je starinski ormar. (In a dark corner of the room, there was an antique wardrobe.)
9. *Mračno* nebo je upozoravalo na dolazak oluje. (The dark sky warned of an approaching storm.)
10. Njegova prošlost je bila *mračna* i puna tajni. (His past was dark and full of secrets.)